piece.track

Class TrackHub

  • java.lang.Object
    • piece.GearedObject
      • piece.track.Track
        • piece.track.TrackHub

  • public class TrackHub
extends Track
    Defines a track hub consisting of three female ports. This class uses geometry.trackshape.TriangleHub to specify the shape of a hub, while this class adds information pertaining to the gear layout and track movement.
